{"tid":801014,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[真唔真呀？] 全線 Intel 的 CPU 低至 Celeron 高至 i7 將會全面缺貨","createTime":"2018-08-31T09:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T10:27:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"291cde2965a84d3fd7b69ec048ee353ab06cf16b","tid":801014,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"[XF突發] 小編收到（路邊社）消息透露，全線Intel 的CPU 低至Celeron 高至 i7 將會全面缺貨。Intel未能提供香港代理所要求的訂單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，究竟同貿易戰有沒有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？這個暫時沒法證實。但好肯定一樣嘢，CPU的價格會因為供應不足而升價。甚至出現有錢無U買的情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/175053_2da462daecac8ba9b3fc42e5a13c5e1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F175053_2da462daecac8ba9b3fc42e5a13c5e1c.png&h=b0d3ce0f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n另外，9月20號將會有NVIDIA 新卡皇RTX2080推出，10月又會有 Intel新晶片組Z390主機板。届時在CPU不足的情況下，而又想組裝新電腦的朋友仔們，真的是（頭痕）了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n另外我們在早前爆料的 i9-9900K、i7-9700K、i5-9600K  CPU推出時間表是2019的Q1，但在其後在很多網站上都說是是今年的10月份推出。因此我們再幫各位（腦友）查詢一下，消息人仕說Intel暫定應該會在下年Q1才上市。所以現在各位想組裝新電腦的朋友，自己計計數吧。<br />\n<br />\n究竟AMD RYZEN 會否在這段缺貨時間再次強攻香港市場？還是Intel 會（咋咋林） 解決這個缺貨問題？我們只有兩個字送給大家 （ LM ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/237469163395167/posts/493121697829911/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F237469163395167%2Fposts%2F493121697829911%2F&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b9a81fb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/237469163395167/posts/493121697829911/</a>"},{"pid":"6bb697d5a5480cfa4962a29e6459d665832fb4bf","tid":801014,"uid":30085,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"期待手持i7就可以有西屌的日子"},{"pid":"95601da81fb81200a6809ebf4f406ed6471ef4e2","tid":801014,"uid":27850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"屌，諗住一兩個月後砌機，睇黎而加要去買定粒U先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab026b8ca58f4c22ed914717f7297fe94798d4a","tid":801014,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外我們在早前爆料的 <span style=\"color: red;\">i9-9900K、i7-9700K、i5-9600K CPU</span>推出時間表是2019的Q1，但在其後在很多網站上都說是是今年的10月份推出。因此我們再幫各位（腦友）查詢一下，消息人仕說Intel暫定應該會在<span style=\"color: red;\">下年Q1才上市</span>。所以現在各位想組裝新電腦的朋友，自己計計數吧。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727d7bbe640c8559be48db04ad40cc66fe1abea2","tid":801014,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:11:02.000Z","msg":"照忍，驚條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248fe47ca57c2906eedb0808a0fb0eb7ca954cd2","tid":801014,"uid":11598,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"係時候轉會<br />\nRyzen R7 2700x 等待各位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726120a5d86ae639ceeca25f935c8aef435d22f4","tid":801014,"uid":33714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[XF突發] 小編收到（路邊社）消息透露，全線Intel 的CPU 低至Celeron 高至 i7 將會全面缺貨。Intel未能提供香港代理所要求的訂單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，究竟同貿易戰有沒有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？這個暫時沒法證實。但好肯定一樣嘢，CPU的價格會因為供應不足而升價。甚至出現有錢無U買的情況<img src=\"/assets/f